texts.Settings:Security.TokenDesc: The user token, (https://tui.juhe.cn/setup) in the center of the personal page views.
texts.Features:TuiJuheEnableDesc: Enable to enable the application to have TuiJuhe capabilities.
texts.Features:MessageEnableDesc: Enable so that apps will have the ability to be pushed notification via TuiJuhe.
texts.Features:Message.SendLimitDesc: Set to limit the amount of TuiJuhe message push.
texts.Features:Message.SendLimitIntervalDesc: Set the TuiJuhe message limit period (time scale: hours). Message sending frequency (request limit) : The rate does not exceed 50 times per unit hour.
